     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs tddui-encounter-type</b></p><a name=\"tddui-encounter-type\"> </a><a name=\"hctddui-encounter-type\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\"/><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><p>Ce jeu de valeur (ValueSet) inclut les codes selon les règles suivantes :</p><ul><li>Importe tous les codes contenu dans <a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.1.0/ValueSet-fr-core-vs-encounter-type.html\">FR Core ValueSet Encounter type</a></li><li>Importe tous les codes contenu dans <a href=\"ValueSet-tddui-serafin.html\">TDDUI SERAFIN</a></li><li>Importe tous les codes contenu dans <a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/terminologies/1.11.1/ValueSet-jdv-type-evenement-ssiad-cisis.html\">JDV Type Evenement Ssiad CISIS</a></li><li>Inclut tous les codes définis dans <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-data-absent-reason.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/data-absent-reason</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 1.0.0\"> version ?1.0.0</span></li></ul></div><div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet tddui-encounter-type</b></p><a name=\"en-tddui-encounter-type\"> </a><a name=\"en-hctddui-encounter-type\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\"/><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profile: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Import all the codes that are contained in <a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.1.0/ValueSet-fr-core-vs-encounter-type.html\">FR Core ValueSet Encounter type</a></li><li>Import all the codes that are contained in <a href=\"ValueSet-tddui-serafin.html\">TDDUI SERAFIN</a></li><li>Import all the codes that are contained in <a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/terminologies/1.11.1/ValueSet-jdv-type-evenement-ssiad-cisis.html\">JDV Type Evenement Ssiad CISIS</a></li><li>Include all codes defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-data-absent-reason.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/data-absent-reason</code></a><span title=\"Version is explicitly stated to be 1.0.0\"> version ?1.0.0</span></li></ul></div></div>"
